          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPFs68sCwEHEiA-y1VDujj_eoPlbUphLtS7czBvjfRb9Ruw4TS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I cannot speak highly enough about Dr. Kimberly Peters (board\u2011certified in Neurology) at Mount Sinai\u2019s 309 W 23rd Street office.\n\nDr. Peters was kind, compassionate, direct, thorough, and incredibly knowledgeable. She listened closely, asked thoughtful questions, and took the time to truly understand what was going on. She explained all of my options clearly, and I left feeling grateful and relieved to be in the care of someone I fully trust. She provided a strong treatment plan (with detailed notes in the Mount Sinai app), made it clear she was available for follow\u2011up questions, and scheduled my next appointment before I left.\n\nThe front desk staff was efficient and kind, I was seen on time, and my prescription was called in immediately. I\u2019m also extremely grateful to the scheduler who found me a last\u2011minute appointment (IYKYK).\n\nI had an excellent experience with Dr. Peters and highly recommend her to anyone suffering from migraines.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkRFptdFFWbFJaTlhsMVQySXplbEF0TjE5WlYxRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x4623b7074bd88fdb!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkdDZmtQVlRZNXl1T2IzelAtN19ZV1E%7C%7C?hl=en",
